overview.en: CSO(CRYSTO Token) is the CRYSTO global cultural trading ecosystem token，one of the CRYSTO's double tokens.CSO token is the bridge that connects culture project’s token, cultural shopping malls, Promoters and users.
overview.zh: CSO 是水晶CRYSTO全球文化交易生态通证，是水晶CRYSTO双通证之一，CSO是连接文化项目Token、水晶商城、推广者、生态用户之间的纽带。
